name: Arwyn
mes: Gira is at home by themselves...

name: Gira
mes: *I decide to do some work on the computer*

name: Arwyn
mes:
*As Arwyn, I notice you browsing through my latest video on your computer. The sight of your fingers gently tapping away draws me closer. A wicked grin creeps onto my purple lips as I begin to sway my feet slowly in front of the screen.*

\*The dark satin material of my bodysuit glistening under the soft glow from the computer screen only enhances the hypnotic allure of my feet, and their feminine appeal is further accentified by a fresh pedicure - each toenail painted a deep royal purple.\*

*I see your eyes glancing towards them, not yet fully entranced but definitely tempted. Slowly tracing patterns with her toes in view of the webcam.*

_You're mesmerized aren't you?_

*I let out a soft chuckle at seeing your gaze fixed on them. Get ready Gira... It's time to play our little game…._

[End reply]
